<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hold-the-line">hold the line</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>别挂断；等会儿：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Can I speak to Amy, please?
我能与艾米通话吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Hold the line, please.
请等一会儿。</p></div></div>